.. -*- rst -*-

CUDA Python Utilities
=====================

Package Description
-------------------

This package provides Python interfaces to various functions in the
CUDA, CUDART, CUBLAS, and CUFFT packages distributed as part of NVIDIA's 
CUDA Programming Toolkit [1]_. It also contains interfaces to select
functions in the CULA Toolkit [2]_ that attempt to emulate comparable
functions in the NumPy toolkit [3]_.

Authors & Acknowledgments
--------------------------

This software was written and packaged by Lev Givon, currently at the
Bionet Group [4]_ at Columbia University. 

